r until I got a call from them telling me to take my daughter to the E.R. because she tried to kill herself. She had over 80 razor blade cuts on her forearms. THEN all of a sudden the school started listening. AFTER I threatened a lawsuit. All of a sudden the realized I was right all school year. Last I heard, 3 kids were suspended for 1 week. And they brag about zero tolerance. Yeah, we put her in a private school &amp; her graduating class will be roughly 24 kids. So,,,, if any of you PARENTS were in my position, would you do the same thing? public schools will only improve if ALL of the childrens parents get involved. Stop blaming your kids bad attitude on the school. Your the parent..... start parenting. Your parents didnt tolerate you lying, bullying, talking back to adults. So why do you allow YOUR kids to do it? "/><type4:DocumentMetaData xmi:id="13" sofa="1" begin="0" end="1124" language="en" documentId="3718" isLastSegment="false"/><types:WebArgumentMetadata xmi:id="24" sofa="1" begin="0" end="0" author="1pissed off dad" date="Aug 29, 2013 6:43PM" docType="artcomment" origUrl="http://living.msn.com/family-parenting/the-family-room-blog-post?post=ab228ffc-1e99-4b37-a7b8-0b6a4c3fb240" topic="public-private-schools" thumbsUp="27" thumbsDown="0" origId="3718" notes="" title="Is it wrong to send kids to private school?"/><type6:Paragraph xmi:id="39" sofa="1" begin="0" end="1124"/><cas:View sofa="1" members="13 24 39"/></xmi:XMI>